    <p>Ku­dos to Ms Ly­dia Chin Kai Jie for demon­strat­ing how prin­ci­ples should al­ways tri­umph over prof­its (A tu­tor’s thoughts: Choose study-life bal­ance for kids, Nov 27).</p>
    <p>Her ad­vice to a par­ent that her child did not need more lessons showed her ded­i­ca­tion to her stu­dents, not to the eco­nomics of her pro­fes­sion.</p>
    <p>That is an ad­mirable qual­ity that pro­fes­sion­als in other fields can em­u­late.</p>
    <p>Thank you, Ms Chin.</p>
    <p>Lee Seong Wee</p>


